snippet.title: While The Iron's Hot - Official Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description: See gameplay, the world, and more from While The Iron's Hot in this trailer for the game. While The Iron's Hot will be available in Q4 2023 on PC, Nintendo Switch, Xbox Series X/S Xbox One, PlayStation 5, and PlayStation 4.
